ActPublic Service Rearrangement and Transfer of Duties Act
SubjectTransfer of Duties Order
PrecisOrder Transferring from the Minister of La Francophonie to the Minister of Economic Development and Official Languages the powers, duties and functions of (a) the Minister of La Francophonie under the CANADIAN TOURISM COMMISSION ACT that were transferred to that Minister by Order in Council P.C. 2018-1016 of July 18, 2018; and (b) the Minister of La Francophonie under the OFFICIAL LANGUAGES ACT that were transferred to that Minister by Order in Council P.C. 2018-1017 of July 18, 2018.
